title: Blessed to Play Cursed to Golf
description:
This week, at least three of us dirty dogs are fulfilling our every fantasy by putting our way through purgatory in Cursed to Golf! Also, we dump out the mailbag again, and dive into it like so many leaves. 

Also discussed: Minecraft, Journey, Return of the Obra Dinn, Desert Golfing, Her Story, Contradiction, Pokemon Go, Going outside, Poinpy, Gigabash, Rollerdome
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (Russ Frushtick, Chris Plante, Griffin McElroy, Justin McElroy)
